metadata.name: Hello,Trefle
metadata.description:
This girl is my original character named Trefle.
This character is filled with a lot of my love.
She lives over the rainbow. She is a guide for lost souls.

A very important point is that with her are two small birds that I have.
I love my little birds dearly, but one day I will have to say goodbye to them.
I have created an angel girl who can stay with us to express our love and affection forever and ever.
I would like to continue to draw illustrations of Trefle and little birds. Please keep an eye on me.
